data.description: This elegant single family home sits in desirable Settlers Pass within the city of Killeen.  Chaparral High School and Central Texas College are closely by for access to those educational institutions.  Thoughtfully landscaped grounds invite you into the beautiful upkept residence. Upon entrance, you are warmly greeted by hardwood floors, fresh paint, and a bright and open floor plan seamlessly connecting the kitchen to the living room and dining room.  Meticulous attention to detail is presented in the kitchen with new granite countertops, freshly finished cabinets, and brand-name appliances. Adjacent from the comfortable living room and fireplace, is the dining/entertainment areas.  Across from here, there is an oversized master bedroom with a sitting area, a walk-in closet, and a separate shower/gardent tub.   The backyard has a covered deck and a nice area to sit and relax after a long, tough day!  BEAUTIFUL home, come on in!!!
